        "Engineering: Speed ГўвЂ вЂќ Precision (fast but rough ГўвЂ вЂќ slow but accurate)",
        "Project Management: Cost ГўвЂ вЂќ Quality ГўвЂ вЂќ Time (iron triangle)",
        "Economics: Inflation ГўвЂ вЂќ Unemployment (Phillips curve)",
        "Computer Science: Time complexity ГўвЂ вЂќ Space complexity",
        "Biology: r-strategy ГўвЂ вЂќ K-strategy (many offspring vs few cared-for)",
